      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. DELTA SANDS turned in a moderate performance last time when eighth at Casino over 411m behind Phantom Juliet (24.61) in a Grade 5. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Worth another chance. 7. LOLLIPOP VALLEY missed the hat-trick last start when second and beaten 1.5 lengths (20.24) last time at this track. Form here is sound including three wins. Expected to feature again. 2. MID CITY BOSS is a smart beginner who has shown good improvement at his last two starts, the latest scoring at this track over 350m. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Has definite claims. 6. GENOVESE was in the money last start here at this trip - likely to feature again.\",\"runners\":[1,7,2,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
